{
  "id": "638d587bf2e94c002015c620",
  "title": "主語を大きくして殴る",
  "created": 1670207614,
  "updated": 1670208230,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "638d587bf2e94c002015c620",
      "text": "主語を大きくして殴る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670207614,
      "updated": 1670207618
    },
    {
      "id": "638d5882aff09e000089d03f",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/3cce7c11562dfadcb18cfebe5ab8da75]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670207619,
      "updated": 1670207622
    },
    {
      "id": "638d5885aff09e000089d041",
      "text": "例:「私はそれが不快だ」→「社会はそれを許さない」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670207622,
      "updated": 1670207795
    },
    {
      "id": "638d592faff09e000089d044",
      "text": "　曖昧で大きな概念を人であるかのように表現して攻撃する現象",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670207791,
      "updated": 1670207799
    },
    {
      "id": "638d5939aff09e000089d045",
      "text": "　　[誤った擬人法]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670207802,
      "updated": 1670207809
    },
    {
      "id": "638d5885aff09e000089d040",
      "text": "　[主語の大きい発言]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670207622,
      "updated": 1670207644
    },
    {
      "id": "638d589caff09e000089d043",
      "text": "　[攻撃]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670207645,
      "updated": 1670207658
    },
    {
      "id": "638d5891aff09e000089d042",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670207634,
      "updated": 1670207634
    },
    {
      "id": "638d595aaff09e000089d046",
      "text": "子供の「[先生に言いつけてやる]」と構造が似ている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670207834,
      "updated": 1670208119
    },
    {
      "id": "638d596baff09e000089d048",
      "text": "　この場合、先生は人間",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670207851,
      "updated": 1670207914
    },
    {
      "id": "638d59aaaff09e000089d049",
      "text": "　攻撃を代行しているわけではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670207914,
      "updated": 1670208129
    },
    {
      "id": "638d5a81aff09e000089d04b",
      "text": "　　先生の価値観で「叱るべきか」を判断して、必要なら叱ってる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670208129,
      "updated": 1670208129
    },
    {
      "id": "638d5a82aff09e000089d04c",
      "text": "　　それを子供が理解しているかは別",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670208131,
      "updated": 1670208139
    },
    {
      "id": "638d59e9aff09e000089d04a",
      "text": "　　先生の価値観を内面化して、告げ口の成功率が高まった子供もいるだろう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670207978,
      "updated": 1670208158
    },
    {
      "id": "638d5a8daff09e000089d04d",
      "text": "　自分が告げ口して先生に叱られる人を見ることによって「強い立場」「[正義]」を味わっていた人は、大人になって「先生」が失われた時に「[力を失った]」と感じるのだろう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670208142,
      "updated": 1670208199
    },
    {
      "id": "638d595baff09e000089d047",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670207836,
      "updated": 1670207836
    },
